description:
## Sheet Stats - Statistics and score of Excel workbook

![Screenshot of Sheet Stats](https://www.japplis.com/sheet-stats/images/sheet-stats-screenshot.png)

Sheet stats will compute how complex your excel files are and give a global score. 
        You can share this score with you colleagues to see who created the most complex Excel files.
        Data used to compute the complexity are number of sheets, number of fonts, number of cells, number of cell types, number of unique formulas, number of unique values and number of charts and images.
summary: Statistics and score of Excel workbook
